    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Practical & Dependable \u2014 A Smart Buy for the Everyday Driver! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably and handles your daily commute without a fuss! You'll notice some cosmetic wear inside and out, as you'd expect from a well-used car, but the fundamentals are solid. If you're looking for honest, no-frills transportation at a sensible price, this one deserves a look. Come take it for a spin \u2014 it just might be exactly what you need!",
