    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a bare-bones budget option? This vehicle is priced to reflect its poor condition \u2014 it has significant visible wear, body damage, and mechanical issues that will need attention. It's a great candidate for a mechanically inclined buyer or someone looking for parts. Priced honestly and transparently so you know exactly what you're getting!",
