    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget-friendly ride to get you from point A to point B? This vehicle is priced to reflect its true condition \u2014 it's a well-used car that shows significant wear both inside and out. The interior has seen better days, and the exterior carries its fair share of bumps and scratches earned over the years. Mechanically, it runs, but you should expect it may need some attention and repairs down the road. If you're handy with cars or just need something basic on a tight budget, this could be your opportunity! Sold as-is at a price that reflects exactly what you're getting.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 it is offered as-is and buyers should have clear, realistic expectations before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear including deep scratches, dents, rust spots, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn throughout, with damaged upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general deterioration consistent with heavy use and age. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect repairs to be necessary, and a pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone seeking a project vehicle, or a buyer with a very tight budget who understands the trade-offs involved. No warranties or representations beyond what is described here are implied.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered at $16,500, and that price honestly reflects its fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but comes with some noticeable wear and imperfections that a discerning buyer should be aware of. The exterior shows visible scratches, dings, and possibly some paint fading or minor rust spots consistent with its age and use. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 expect faded upholstery, scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of daily use. Mechanically, the car gets the job done, though it may have some deferred maintenance or minor issues that should be addressed in the near term. This is not a turn-key, worry-free vehicle, but it is a solid option for a budget-conscious buyer who wants reliable basic transportation and doesn't mind putting in a little effort to bring it up to better shape. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you know exactly what you're getting.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 and we mean that without reservation. The exterior is flawless: the paint gleams with a deep, showroom-quality shine, free of scratches, chips, swirl marks, or any blemishes whatsoever. Every panel is perfectly aligned, the trim is pristine, and the glass is crystal clear with no chips or cracks. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 the seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces look and feel as though they've barely been touched. There is no odor, no staining, and no wear to speak of. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, all fluids are at proper levels, and the mechanical systems are operating in perfect order. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and it shows at every turn. If you're looking for a car that feels genuinely new despite its age, this is a rare find. A thorough inspection is welcomed and encouraged \u2014 we're confident it will speak for itself.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    }
